Invocation Name: luther chips
des:
Luther College Chips is made for students, by students, and because of students, and this Alexa skill is no exception.

Hear the latest from Luther Chips without having to turn a page. Simply ask for the most recent article, or the most recent article in a section.

Stories will be visually displayed on devices with screens.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
